25	    def formula(tax_unit, period, parameters):
26	        itemizes = tax_unit("tax_unit_itemizes", period)
27	        sd = tax_unit("ga_standard_deduction", period)
28	        # 48-7-27(a)(1) states:
29	        # "Either the sum of all itemized nonbusiness deductions used in computing
30	        #  such taxpayerโs federal taxable income or..."
31	        p = parameters(period).gov.irs.deductions
32	        itemized = add(tax_unit, period, p.itemized_deductions)
